The paper deals with monitoring Linear Time Logic (LTL) specifications, which is a topic related to formal methods and verification. Therefore, cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category. The paper also proposes a two-step approach that involves computing and predicting, which are topics related to programming languages (cs.PL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with monitoring over finite traces, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper deals with formal languages (cs.FL) since it deals with LTL specifications.
